OL,3,CKeir Starmer condemns attack on Gurkha
OL,4,Cveterans who were told 'go home'
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has condemned an
OL,7,Fattack on Gurkha veterans in
OL,8,FAldershot, describing it as "utterly
OL,9,Fdisgraceful".
OL,11,FLocal MP Alex Baker said the incident
OL,12,Fwhere veterans were told to "go home"
OL,13,Foccurred near a war memorial.
OL,15,FIn the Commons, Ms Baker pressed the
OL,16,FPrime Minister to resolve issues
OL,17,Fsurrounding Gurkha pensions, to which
OL,18,Fhe responded that work is continuing.
