OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782386302
OL,3,CKeir Starmer condemns attack on Gurkha
OL,4,Cveterans who were told 'go home'
OL,6,F"We stand with our Gurkhas, who have
OL,7,Fmade an incredible contribution to our
OL,8,Farmed forces and continue to do so.
OL,10,F"On Gurkha pensions, ministers have
OL,11,Fmet her, veterans, and the government
OL,12,Fof Nepal for constructive discussions.
OL,13,FThese will continue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@UO]
